bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.filter

Interface BRule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BRuleImplem

    public interface BRule
extends Cloneable
    This interface defines a BRule. It is a basic element of a BFilter defining a single constraint on SRHit/SRHSP attributes. A rule is made of three parts: an accessor, an operator and a value. They are used to create a simple boolean expression such as <accessor> <operator> <value>.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
